oppSpot Modernization Strategy                                                          │ │
│ │                                                                                         │ │
│ │ Phase 1: Real-Time Infrastructure (Foundation) 🏗                                       │ │
│ │                                                                                         │ │
│ │ 1. Implement Supabase Realtime Subscriptions                                            │ │
│ │   - Live deal updates, notifications, collaborative presence                            │ │
│ │   - Replace in-memory event bus with persistent event store                             │ │
│ │   - Add WebSocket connections for multiplayer features                                  │ │
│ │ 2. Stream Processing Architecture                                                       │ │
│ │   - Add Redis/Upstash for event streaming & caching                                     │ │
│ │   - Implement worker pool architecture (BullMQ/Inngest)                                 │ │
│ │   - Move from batch to stream processing for lead scoring                               │ │
│ │ 3. Enhanced Database Layer                                                              │ │
│ │   - Add pgvector to Supabase for AI embeddings                                          │ │
│ │   - Implement TimescaleDB extension for time-series metrics                             │ │
│ │   - Add Redis for caching, sessions, rate limiting                                      │ │
│ │                                                                                         │ │
│ │ Phase 2: Modern AI Capabilities 🤖                                                      │ │
│ │                                                                                         │ │
│ │ 1. RAG Implementation                                                                   │ │
│ │   - Add vector database (Pinecone/Supabase pgvector)                                    │ │
│ │   - Implement semantic search for deals, companies, stakeholders                        │ │
│ │   - Company profile embeddings for similarity matching                                  │ │
│ │ 2. AI Agent Orchestration                                                               │ │
│ │   - Integrate LangChain/Vercel AI SDK                                                   │ │
│ │   - Build autonomous agents for research, qualification, outreach                       │ │
│ │   - Implement streaming AI responses (not blocking calls)                               │ │
│ │ 3. Advanced Scoring Models                                                              │ │
│ │   - Add predictive lead scoring with ML pipelines                                       │ │
